arguments.input_description: The image shows a tic-tac-toe game in progress. There is text at the top saying "Let's play tic-tac-toe!" and "I'll be X." The game board is drawn with a 3x3 grid, and there is one X placed in the top-left square. The board is located approximately at coordinates x:100, y:150, width:200, height:200.
arguments.output_description: I will draw an O in the center square of the tic-tac-toe board, sized appropriately to fit within the grid cell at approximately x:165, y:215, width:70, height:70.
